# Roofline analysis results and plots (generated by roofline_analysis.py)
#
# After running: python profiling/roofline_analysis.py
#   - roofline_results.csv  : arithmetic intensity, achieved GFLOPS/GB/s, memory-bound flag
#   - roofline_results.json: same data in JSON
#   - roofline_plot.png    : roofline curve with memory-bound (blue) vs compute-bound (orange) points
